profile_summary: I'm Midhunraj, a web developer with a strong foundation in JavaScript, TypeScript, and backend development, currently working on angular.js projects. With a portfolio of 27 public repositories and a growing professional network, I'm passionate about leveraging my technical skills to deliver innovative solutions. I'm excited to collaborate and contribute to open-source projects, and you can find me on LinkedIn and Instagram to learn more about my work and interests.
